Mbembo Bemba, Client Coverage Manager | Katanga Region at Standard Bank DRC chats to Laura Cornish, Editor-In-Chief of Mining Review Africa at DRC Mining Week 2022. Highlights include the strong attendance at the event, the value Standard Bank DRC brings to the local market, the focus on tech metals and how it is supporting the full mining ecosystem. This video can be viewed in French by adjusting the closed caption and setting options.